01:02:07,844 --> 01:02:10,544
時計の針のように
Like the hands of a clock

847
01:02:10,644 --> 01:02:16,944
刻んだ思い出たち 広げた
I spread the memories I've carved out

848
01:02:18,644 --> 01:02:23,144
戻れないから また 愛しさが募る
Since I can't go back, again my love for you grows

849
01:02:25,644 --> 01:02:30,144
キミに逢いたいよ
I want to see you

850
01:02:40,544 --> 01:02:45,444
二人で温めた 大切なストーリー
The precious story the two of us nurtured

851
01:02:45,844 --> 01:02:50,644
遠くまで続いた 果てない道
The endless road that stretched far away

852
01:02:51,244 --> 01:02:55,844
疲れたら代わるから そう言ってくれた
'I'll take over if you're tired,' you said

853
01:02:56,044 --> 01:03:00,844
優しさに触れて見えた
Touching your kindness, I could see

854
01:03:01,444 --> 01:03:06,144
受け入れてくれたこと
That you accepted me

855
01:03:06,744 --> 01:03:11,844
忘れない 嬉しくて満ちた日々
I won't forget the days filled with joy

856
01:03:14,444 --> 01:03:17,344
雨上がりの胸に
In my heart after the rain

857
01:03:17,444 --> 01:03:23,144
架かった虹のように綺麗な
Beautiful like a rainbow stretching across

858
01:03:25,644 --> 01:03:30,344
キミからの言葉 一つ一つが
Each and every word from you

859
01:03:32,544 --> 01:03:37,444
今も 宝物
Is still a treasure now

860
01:03:46,944 --> 01:03:51,744
支えてくれたから
Because you supported me

861
01:03:52,344 --> 01:03:57,144
輝ける この気持ち届けよう
I'll deliver these shining feelings

862
