the one we showed at the very beginning...

889
01:07:09,132 --> 01:07:19,132
ノエルちゃんとラミィたんとの3人の「初恋大戦争」のMV公開があって、
...the MV for "Hatsukoi Daisensou" by the three of us with Noel-chan and Lamy-tan will be released.

890
01:07:19,132 --> 01:07:24,132
そのあとメン限で、
After that, in the membership-only stream,

891
01:07:24,132 --> 01:07:32,132
ちょっとライブと撮影会の続きとか、ちょっとね、メン限でしか見れない...
we'll have the continuation of the live and photo session, and something you can only see in membership...

892
01:07:32,132 --> 01:07:43,132
シチュエーションドラマとかやるので、ぜひぜひ気になる人は見に行ってくださーい！
...like a situation drama, so if you're interested, please come watch it!

893
01:07:43,132 --> 01:07:47,132
それではまた後でお会いしましょう！
Well then, let's meet again later!

894
01:07:47,132 --> 01:07:51,132
おつかれーと！
Otsu-kare-to!

895
01:07:51,132 --> 01:07:56,732
はむっ、ちゅっ！
*Ham, Chu!*

